{"tid":1666264,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【抗暴之戰】警方擬改用中國製催淚彈","createTime":"2019-10-21T02:15:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T02:15:33.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c86d2d59b88e6b900d34a31a3bc7251f0ad9f7f6","tid":1666264,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:15:33.000Z","msg":"昨日（20日）九龍多區爆發警民衝突，防暴警員發射多枚催淚彈。《蘋果》記者發現，其中一枚催淚彈落在馬路油漆上，懷疑因為彈頭太高溫而融掉馬路上的油漆，情況極為罕見。記者觀察指，<span style=\"color: red;\">此款催淚彈較過去警方使用的催淚彈爆炸時更大聲，煙味更濃烈，有機會釋出更多有毒物質</span>。<br />\n<br />\n自6月中的警民衝突起，防暴警察均極頻密地發射大量催淚彈，至今已經使用超過5,000枚催淚彈。不過原本為香港警隊供應催淚彈的英國，已經宣佈拒絕向香港供貨。<span style=\"color: red;\">警方承認，最近曾向中國購入「國產催淚彈」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n《南華早報》早前引述消息，指警方的催淚彈存貨已無法應付現有需求，最近改向中國購入大批催淚彈，與解放軍反恐部隊使用的型號相同，聲稱其爆發時間較快，煙霧更密集，令目標更難及時作反應。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191021/60176377?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3bJJTLK-T-JKUlES7R67i5EyD5n8LEwvp7cEhvfuEpZgPk2sEb5OutYbs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191021%2F60176377%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3bJJTLK-T-JKUlES7R67i5EyD5n8LEwvp7cEhvfuEpZgPk2sEb5OutYbs&d=IZFSAkWTwbXSesVVmoeERQHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=08c4a7e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191021%2F60176377%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3bJJTLK-T-JKUlES7R67i5EyD5n8LEwvp7cEhvfuEpZgPk2sEb5OutYbs&h=3ce1e129\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191021/60176377?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3bJJTLK-T-JKUlES7R67i5EyD5n8LEwvp7cEhvfuEpZgPk2sEb5OutYbs</a>"}]}